	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">今日娱乐：篮协公布 CBA 改革方案，Wii U 后年停产</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-28 09:57:22 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">2</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
<!-- 传入参数：article -->

<a href="/articles/26083.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/26083/indexMediumPc2/26083.jpg?1461745652" alt="优衣库和 KAWS 的联名系列开卖，KAWS自己怎么看？">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/19/medium/19.png?1411569539" alt="时尚">
			<span>时尚</span>
		</p>
